      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu tad/ ak KUNGS Ze-\nbaot! kas tu to Taifnu pahr-\nvaudi/ kas tahß Jhſtis un Sir-\ndis reds/ Laid es tawu Atreep-\nſchann pee teem redſu. Jo teiv\neſmu es fawu Teetas Leetu pa-\nwehlejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Dfeedajt tam KUNgam/\nflawejeet to KUNGU/ jo wiꞥſch\nirr ta Nabbaga Dwehfeli atpe-\nſtijs no to Launadarritajo Roh-\nkas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nolahdeta laid irr ta\nDeena/ eekſch ka es efinu dſim-\nmis/ ta Deena/ eekſch ka manna\nMahte manni irr dſemdejſi/ un\nlai ta ne irr fwehttita.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nolahdehts laid irr tas\nWihrs/ kas mannam Tehwam\nirr ſtabſtijs / un faſzijs: Tew\nirr weens jauns Dehls dſimmis/\nar tahdu Preezivu winnu eeprce-\nzinadams.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir tas pats Wihrs laid\ntee ka' tee Pillsfahti/ ko tas\nKUNGS irr apgahtis/ un Win-\nxam ne irr ſchehl bijis / un laid\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "tas agri dfird weenu Brehtſcha-\nnu/ un puß Deena weenu Kleeg-\nschanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka ne eſti tu manni no-\nkawis no Mahtes Meeſahm? ka\nmanna Mahte buhtu mans Kapß\nbijuti/ un winnas Meeſas muh-\nscham buhtu gruhtas palieku-\nschas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kapehz eſimu es no Mah-\ntes Meeſahm iſgahjts/ Gruhtu-\nmu un Sird·Ehſus redſeht/ un\nka mannas Deenas ar Raunu\ntohp pawadditas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XXI. Nodalla.\nZedekijus tas Kehniſch leek to Praweetu zaue\nJſubutiteem waizaht / arrig Deews winnuß\niſglahbs : 1. Jeremijus atbilde/ ne: 3. Un\ndohd tam Kehnimam to Padohmu/ laid\nwinſch pats ar teem kaudim labbiß Prahtis\nNebukadNezaaram padohdahß: 8. 9.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Chis irr tas Wahrdß/\nSas notikke us Jeremiju\nno ta KUNGA/ kad tas\nKehniſch Zedekijus pee winna\nfuhtija Paſſuru Malkijus Deh-\nlu/ un Zewaniju/ Maëſejus Deh-\nlu/ to Preesteri/ un faſzijsa:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Waiza jelle to KUNGU\nvar mums/ jo NebukadRezars\ntas Kehniſch no Babeles kazro\nprett mums. Jaſchu darrihs tas\nKUNGS ar mums pehz fa-\nwein Brihnuneem/ ka tas no\nmums atſtahjahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad faſzijs Jeremijus uhs\nteen: Ta buhs jums Zedeki-\njum faſziht:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta faſka tas KUNGS/\ntas Iſraëta Deews: Raugi/ es\n"
    }
